When editing a page, you can send the new content using the "Ctrl S" key sequence.

"Ctrl S" means pushing the Ctrl key on the keyboard and then the S key (and have them both pressed as a result).

If you press the "Esc" key, it's like clicking on the "Cancel" buttons (ie changes are removed).

